her feet on a stepstool.

00:03:09.889 --> 00:03:11.750
Children who make art for the 

00:03:11.750 --> 00:03:16.250
first-time often show a great interest
in this form of self-expression and if

00:03:16.250 --> 00:03:20.279
encourage can learn to draw at a
very early age.

00:03:20.279 --> 00:03:23.439
This is a drawing by a blind girl

00:03:23.439 --> 00:03:24.969
aged eight. 

00:03:24.969 --> 00:03:26.809
How come she draw so well?

00:03:26.809 --> 00:03:30.529
Well from the age of two or three

00:03:30.529 --> 00:03:33.319
she was encouraged to draw

00:03:33.319 --> 00:03:34.529
by her mother.

