then i wouldn't be a respecting them as
people. The most important aspect of any

00:04:14.209 --> 00:04:15.430
art making class

00:04:15.430 --> 00:04:17.599
is very simple

00:04:17.599 --> 00:04:22.460
anything goes. In our sessions where they
just focus on making art

00:04:22.460 --> 00:04:24.069
it is all about them 

00:04:24.069 --> 00:04:25.270
and they can do

00:04:25.270 --> 00:04:26.499
nothing wrong

00:04:26.499 --> 00:04:28.589
and that's a therapeutic part.

00:04:28.589 --> 00:04:33.830
There can't be rules in artmaking. It is
something that comes from the soul.

